Package dataManagers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApproverClaimListManager
    The ApproverClaimListManager is the base class for all elastic web server connections which allow an application to draw claims from the webserver onto the approver's claims list
    ClaimantClaimListManager  
    ClaimListManager
    ClaimListManager is the abstract base class for connecting to the webserver which allow the application to serialize and load user claims onto the claims list A ClaimListManager object encapsulates the state information needed for the various online/offline loading operations that app supports.
    ConnectionChangeReceiver
    from http://stackoverflow.com/a/1785300 March 30 ConnectionChangerReceiver is a network listener that detects the connectivity of the device and saves to the online/offline location using the ClaimListManager
    HomeLocationManager
    Will provide an interface to save the user's home location to the disk and to the web.
    ReceiptPhotoManager  
    TagListManager
    Provides an interface to save the associated TagList to the disk and to the web server.
